title: Kostars - Klassics with a K mp3
description:
"Kostars duo Viv and Jill are best known as dedicated members of the musical group Luscious Jackson.They began the Kostars one warm, sultry evening in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. The fireflies were circling, the cicadas were singing and magic was in the air. Inspired by life on the road, the gals made a beeline for the woods behind the club with acoustic guitars in hand. As the strumming began, sparks began to fly and songs to form. If you share with the Kostars a love of mellow tones and simple songs, listen to these new sounds and feel that warm summer night float through your speakers." Jack Torso, Winter 1995. Text taken from dedication at the back cover of cd.
